node.title: Woman pictured taking selfie as car sinks into frozen river
node.description: She was standing on top of a car descending into a frozen river.
node.content: ["A Canadian woman who crashed through ice while driving on a frozen river decided rather than trying to abort the sinking car she would snap a selfie.", "The woman was pictured taking photos of herself as the vehicle slowly descended into the Rideau River in Ottawa.", "The National Post reported residents along the river used a kayak to save the driver.", "However, why the woman was driving on the river is unclear.", "Police said the driver was not injured, the National Post reported.\u00a0"]
